{"id": 1147, "genre": 1001, "title": "你因为独自生活而多花了哪些钱？", "description": "不瞒你说，各种电商外卖o2o能活下来都有我一份力。", "record_count": 4437, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160804105343UdNPHw8vKCFlqSum.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-08-05T03:00:57Z", "options": [{"id": 104961, "content": "找对象，花钱，但找对象就是因为单身，所以这个钱算花在自己身上的！", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 705061}, {"id": 104963, "content": "第二份半价。。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 705064}, {"id": 105222, "content": "一个人做饭，结果为了保存剩饭，又买了冰箱。", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 121153}, {"id": 104971, "content": "锅子。。。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 190542}, {"id": 106764, "content": "｢第二杯半价｣", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 280668}, {"id": 104973, "content": "外卖起送不够，得加个不需要的吃的一起送", "image": null, "praise_count": 22, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 705189}, {"id": 105485, "content": "零食？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 607959}, {"id": 105487, "content": "失眠时找深夜陪聊", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 607959}, {"id": 104722, "content": "网购的成本增加，还有吃饭！", "image": "img/option/option/20160806075216pxECPshH8SfwT6yi", "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 693887}, {"id": 104727, "content": "房租，水电费，各种各样的便当费", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 695327}, {"id": 105495, "content": "买青菜的时候总会听到小贩说：再拿一点，你那还不够1块钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 204651}, {"id": 104994, "content": "跟朋友出去吃喝，出去找兼职给中介的费用", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 686529}, {"id": 112163, "content": "煮饭都浪费电", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 741508}, {"id": 104486, "content": "房租", "image": null, "praise_count": 236, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 429917}, {"id": 104488, "content": "由于不需要养家，我就养了游戏开发者 / 公司……", "image": null, "praise_count": 151, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 590050}, {"id": 104744, "content": "电影票与书", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 703348}, {"id": 104489, "content": "房租、日用品、网费、伙食费", "image": null, "praise_count": 261, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 697740}, {"id": 105001, "content": "总觉得我省了些什么，出了狗粮", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 705330}, {"id": 104490, "content": "买了很多根本用不到的东西", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 37125}, {"id": 105770, "content": "第二件半价。。。一人食。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 708134}, {"id": 104491, "content": "一个人出去旅游，住宿成本特别的高！", "image": null, "praise_count": 444, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 36446}, {"id": 105003, "content": "网购伤不起", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 701681}, {"id": 105771, "content": "除了抱着手机 ipa的追剧 剩下的就只有美团外卖 你懂得", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 708147}, {"id": 104492, "content": "当然是狗粮！", "image": null, "praise_count": 131, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 652329}, {"id": 104493, "content": "哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 31, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 659454}, {"id": 104494, "content": "狗粮", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 652329}, {"id": 104495, "content": "买了很多方便食品，多半都会因为忘记吃掉过期，然后再买，如此循环", "image": null, "praise_count": 24, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 645237}, {"id": 104751, "content": "一言不合就开淘宝", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 675350}, {"id": 104496, "content": "吃午餐点两份，对面的没人吃，买情侣装，女装没人穿，充话费，对方只会在朋友圈发条“谁帮我充的，告诉我，我一定嫁给他。”", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 662208}, {"id": 105008, "content": "所有消费性陋习都丝毫没有顾忌，没了约束，只有放纵。\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 705339}, {"id": 104497, "content": "所有代价换舒适，值得！生活用品买了都是自己用，不需要忍受别人看剧公放，不需要为了和谐而忍让或者撕破脸。", "image": null, "praise_count": 118, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 702163}, {"id": 105265, "content": "买不起陪伴", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 705458}, {"id": 104498, "content": "多花？我觉得只要能提高独居生活品质，就值得?", "image": null, "praise_count": 78, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 633090}, {"id": 104499, "content": "一个人可以省去好多钱 例如 我不用请人吃饭 不用买很多我并不是很愿意买的东西  也可以省下来好多时间 去看书等等", "image": null, "praise_count": 54, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 649083}, {"id": 124211, "content": "令我自己開心的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 795616}, {"id": 104500, "content": "食量凑不满想吃的店的起送费，于是只好点多点", "image": null, "praise_count": 422, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 293164}, {"id": 104501, "content": "喜欢的内裤只有情侣款?", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 591216}, {"id": 104502, "content": "没有基友的日常生活，无聊", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 692867}, {"id": 104503, "content": "各种小东西没地方借，只能买", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 315594}, {"id": 105015, "content": "所以就是赶紧结婚，生子哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 694548}, {"id": 104504, "content": "看着单身们尽力找出自己的优越感，略心疼...", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 229827}, {"id": 104505, "content": "并不会多花.反而不用去买一些我根本用不着的东西.也不用依着别人的喜好来委屈自己.", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 703469}, {"id": 105017, "content": "买好了厨具一个人做饭，却三分钟热度，之后扔掉了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 697262}, {"id": 104506, "content": "买了好多卫生纸。。。。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 63, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 681253}, {"id": 104507, "content": "为孤独而吃的钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 68, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 646202}, {"id": 104763, "content": "马云的成功有我一份力", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 53545}, {"id": 105019, "content": "哈哈，自由", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 578269}, {"id": 104509, "content": "一个人开一天空调", "image": null, "praise_count": 278, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 516406}, {"id": 104510, "content": "房租水电煤管理? ", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 203302}, {"id": 104255, "content": "无人分担的房费、打车费", "image": null, "praise_count": 364, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}]}